s such as Publish-Subscribe (Pub/Sub) or Request-Reply with retries, and implement a centralized message broker to facilitate real-time and reliable communication.\n3.  Develop a centralized knowledge base where agents can share critical contextual information and implement a robust context sharing protocol that ensures data consistency and availability across all agents.\n\nOverall, the report provides a comprehensive analysis of the current capabilities of the swarm platform compared to a full multi-agent AI system and recommends actionable improvements to enhance reliability, efficiency, and overall performance.",
